abstract: Mr. Shelby was a titan of motorsports and muscle cars, credited with the Cobra sports car and a number of later collaborations with Ford. Recently, Mr. Shelby’s name appeared on the 2013 Shelby GT500, the most powerful production version of the Ford Mustang. He died on Thursday in Dallas.
